4. I'm NOT REGISTRD to vote

Please accept the terms and conditions to get started
1. Accept & Join
2. Read t&c
3. Quit
Tx 4 joining! We need ur voting ward. Type ur home address & we'll work it out. This is prvt, only ur voting ward will be stored &u will be anonymous
Tnx 4 volunteering 2 be a citizen reporter for the '14 elections! Start by answering questions or report election activity! Dial back in to *120*7692*3# begin!
Make a choice, have a voice, vote! Your inked finger will show everyone that you have voted!
If u haven't already, join thousands of other South Africans and tell us about your experience on election day! Dial*120*4729*1#  It's free to dial!
